title: TBARW EXTRA: Transparent political mapmode - Europa Universalis
description:
TBARW EXTRA: Transparent political mapmode - Europa Universalis IV mod


Extract 7zip to your C:Users[user]Documents Paradox Interactive Europa Universalis IV mod folder


DESCRIPTION
Optional extra for mod "Thick borders and recolored water" 
(Can be used on any mod or default) 

This mod makes mapmodes abit transparent thus showing snow in political mapmode and more visible terrain (more visible mountains and stuff) 

IRONMAN-COMPATIBLE
